# 🌾 SkyRice Global

> **Premium Rice Import, Export, Processing & Polishing Solutions**
>
> Connecting farmers, dealers, businesses, and households with high-quality rice sourced directly from Bihar, India.

---

## 🚀 Live Features

✨ Modern Responsive Landing Page
✨ Rice Import & Export Business Website
✨ Direct Farmer-to-Buyer Network
✨ Product Showcase & Rice Varieties
✨ Interactive Contact & Enquiry Form
✨ Email Integration with EmailJS
✨ Mobile Friendly Design
✨ SEO Optimized Structure
✨ Fast Loading Embedded Images
✨ WhatsApp & Email Contact Support

---

