## ⚙️ Installation

### Clone Repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/skyrice-global.git
```

### Open Project

```bash
cd skyrice-global
```

### Run

Simply open:

```bash
index.html
```

or use VS Code Live Server.

---

## 📧 EmailJS Setup

### 1. Create Account

https://www.emailjs.com

### 2. Create Service

Example:

```text
service_xxxxxx
```

### 3. Create Template

Variables:

```html
{{name}}
{{phone}}
{{email}}
{{location}}
{{role}}
{{type}}
{{company}}
{{variety}}
{{quantity}}
{{visit}}
{{message}}
```

### 4. Get Public Key

Dashboard → Account → API Keys

### 5. Configure

```javascript
emailjs.init("YOUR_PUBLIC_KEY");
```

```javascript
emailjs.send(
  "YOUR_SERVICE_ID",
  "YOUR_TEMPLATE_ID",
  formData
);
```

